
Microservice 1 (Currency Exchange Rate Microservice)
What is the exchange rate of one currency in another
URL : http://localhost:8000/currency-exchange/from/USD/to/INR
Response :
{
	“id” : 1001,
	“from” : “USD”,
	“to” : “INR”,
	“conversionMultiple” : 65.00,
	“environment” : “8000 instance-id”
}


Microservice 2 (Currency Conversion Microservice)
Convert 10 USD into INR
URL : http://localhost:8100/currency-conversion/from/USD/to/INR/quantity/10
Response :
{
	“id” : 1001,
	“from” : “USD”,
	“to” : “INR”,
	“conversionMultiple” : 65.00,
	“quantity” : 10,
	“totalCalculatedAmount” : 650.00,
	“environment” : “8000 instance-id”
}
